These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
6 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, frog, goat, hedgehog, lizard
House: ranch-style, townhouse, modern, gothic-revival, art-deco, colonial
1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the art-deco house is between the owner of the lizard and the ranch-style house##2
5. the gothic-revival house is between the art-deco house and the townhouse house##2
6. the ranch-style house is the owner of the goat##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
8. the colonial house is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Pet           | fish | guinea-pig | lizard | hedgehog | goat    | frog  |
| House   | colonial | townhouse   | gothic-revival       | art-deco        | ranch-style | modern |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, scooter, ship, subway, quad-bike, boat
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: may, august, february, october, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the train##2
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Transport   | scooter | boat | quad-bike | subway | ship | train  |
| Birthday           | november | june  | may | august    | october  | february |

