.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: sports, animation, family, comedy, epic, disaster
There are 6 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, cola, lemonade, coffee, sprite, water
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
6. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
9. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre         | animation | sports | disaster      | epic | comedy | family      |
| Beverage   | cola    | water  | hot-chocolate | coffee   | sprite       | lemonade |

