.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different games are played: scrabble, poker, mah-jongg, canasta, bridge, chess
There are 6 different nationalities: british, russian, nigerian, turkish, australian, indian
1. the nigerian is the person playing canasta##1
2. the indian is on the right of the british##1
3. the australian is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the turkish is the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing scrabble is the british##1
6. the russian is between the british and the person playing chess##2
7. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing chess##1
8. the nigerian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Game        | poker    | chess | mah-jongg | scrabble | bridge | canasta   |
| Nationality   | turkish | australian        | russian  | british     | indian  | nigerian |

