.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-5::.
6 different games are played: go, canasta, mah-jongg, chess, snooker, scrabble
The people have 6 different hobbies: skydiving, camping, collecting, board-games, gardening, cooking
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person playing canasta is between the person playing mah-jongg and the person playing snooker##2
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person playing chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Game   | go   | chess    | scrabble | mah-jongg | canasta | snooker   |
| Hobby         | gardening | skydiving | collecting | cooking | board-games  | camping |

