.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
City: new-york, boston, hannover, prague, hamburg, marseilles
House: colonial, farmhouse, craftsman, art-deco, modern, palace
1. the colonial house is on the left of the modern house##1
2. the palace house is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the palace house is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
7. the craftsman house is the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to prague and the palace house##2
9. the person traveling to new-york is the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| City    | new-york | marseilles | hamburg  | prague      | hannover | boston  |
| House   | farmhouse  | craftsman    | art-deco | colonial | modern | palace |

