.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  security-guard, entrepreneur, manager, nurse, journalist, architect
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: rose, bellflower, lily, tulip, poppy, daisy
1. the person who growstulip is the person who growstulip##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the security-guard##1
3. the security-guard is between the journalist and the nurse##2
4. the nurse is the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the architect is on the left of the nurse##1
6. the journalist is between the person who growstulip and the person who growspoppy##2
7. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
8. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
9. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Job       | architect | nurse | security-guard | journalist | manager | entrepreneur |
| Flower   | lily | daisy    | poppy  | rose    | tulip    | bellflower    |

