.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-8::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, sunflower, bellflower, begonia, aconite
There are 6 different favourite colors: apricot, blood-red, brown, orange, lilac, emerald
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes emerald is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes apricot##2
4. the person who growsbellflower is the person who likes brown##1
5. the person who growssunflower is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsbegonia##2
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Flower           | bellflower | aconite | begonia | sunflower | daisy | amaryllis |
| Color   | brown   | orange   | blood-red         | apricot    | emerald     | lilac     |

