.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, tram, subway, jet-ski, scooter
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, thriller, martial-arts, scientific, zombie, time-travel
 1. the person driving the scooter is the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the person watching family movies is between the person driving the trike and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Transport   | trike   | jet-ski  | skateboard | subway | scooter | tram     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | family | time-travel    | zombie | scientific | martial-arts |

