.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-11::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  project-manager, freelancer, bartender, software-developer, photographer, social-worker
6 different games are played: whist, billiard, poker, monopoly, domino, chess
 1. the software-developer is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 2. the photographer is the person playing domino##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 5. the person playing domino is between the person playing billiard and the bartender##2
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the right of the bartender##1
 8. the software-developer is the person playing whist##1
 9. the project-manager is between the person playing whist and the freelancer##2
10. the software-developer is the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |
| Job         | social-worker   | photographer | bartender       | software-developer | project-manager    | freelancer |
| Game   | billiard | domino  | poker | whist      | monopoly | chess        |

