.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-12::.
There 6 different types of food: zucchini, potato, papaya, lettuce, carrot, cucumber
City: venice, prague, marseilles, colone, edinburgh, liverpool
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 3. the person eating potato is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person eating papaya is between the person eating lettuce and the person traveling to liverpool##2
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person eating carrot##2
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 7. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is the person eating zucchini##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |         3          |      4      |    5    |      6       |
| Food           | potato      | lettuce | papaya | zucchini   | cucumber  | carrot |
| City   | colone | venice  | prague             | liverpool | marseilles | edinburgh       |

