.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, prince, blend, aristoff, cain
House: wooden, modern, townhouse, colonial, cottage, craftsman
1. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
2. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
3. the wooden house is between the aristoff-smoker and the blend-smoker##2
4. the cain-smoker is on the right of the modern house##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the craftsman house##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the modern house##1
7. the colonial house is the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Cigar          | prince | bongani | tiparillo | aristoff    | cain | blend |
| House   | townhouse     | craftsman | colonial   | modern | wooden | cottage |

