.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, spy, horror, documentary, superhero, sports
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, hiking, skydiving, video-games, sudoku, chess
 1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person watching spy movies##2
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's hobby is singing##2
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person watching horror movies##2
 6. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | action | superhero   | horror     | sports       | spy       |
| Hobby    | hiking | video-games   | singing | sudoku | chess | skydiving |

