 4. the person driving the boat is the person who growspoppy##1
 5. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person driving the ship is the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the helicopter is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsamaryllis##2
10. the person who growstulip is the person who growstulip##1

